data.value:
Q: Why don't some mods work? A: Some mods will only work if you are the host of the game. If you still cannot use them please file a bug report.
Q: Why don't some commands work? A: Commands will only work when you are the host or have the "Moderator" permissions in a world
Q: I want to report a bug or suggest a new mod, how do I do that? A: You can report bugs or suggest new features in our Discord Server or on Github which can both be found on the home page.
Q: How do I figure out what a mod does? A: Each option has a Tool Tip that describes what each one does which you can view by hovering over any mod.
Q: I can't connect to my Wii U, what do I do? A: Make sure you are using the Homebrew Launcher, entered the correct IP Address or check your network connection.
